EventItemTitle:
By Council Member Van Bramer:
Pursuant to Rule 11.20(b) of the Council and §20-226 of the New York City Administrative Code, the Council resolves that the action of the Department of Consumer Affairs approving an unenclosed sidewalk café located at 4618 Vernon Blvd., Borough of Queens, Council District 26, Community District 2, Application No. 20205036 TCQ (Dai Hachi Sushi Corporation) shall be subject to review by the Council.
